# Week 5 â€” Day X: IAM Security Dashboard

## Goal
Create a CloudWatch dashboard to visualize IAM security signals from CloudTrail-driven metrics.

## Steps
1. Built dashboard JSON with widgets for:
   - Unauthorized API (time-series)
   - Root logins (single value)
   - IAM changes (single value)
2. Uploaded with `aws cloudwatch put-dashboard`.

## Evidence
```bash
aws cloudwatch describe-dashboards --dashboard-name-prefix "$DASH" \
  --query 'DashboardEntries[0].{Name:DashboardName,LastModified:LastModified}' --output table

aws cloudwatch get-dashboard --dashboard-name "$DASH" \
  --query '{Name:DashboardName,Body:DashboardBody}' --output text | head -n 20
